text: Bajo Boquete is a corregimiento in Boquete District, Chiriquí Province, Panama. It is the seat of Boquete District. It has a land area of and had a population of 4,493 as of 2010, giving it a population density of . Its population as of 1990 was 10,908; its population as of 2000 was 3,833. ==References== Category:Corregimientos of Chiriquí Province es:Bajo Boquete
